- All the nominees will start with 10 points. You vote by substrating 1 point each from 2 nominees and adding 1 point to 1 nominee. If the point reach 0, the nominee is eliminated. The last nominee will own a title.

- You can only vote 1 in every 24 hours and you can't vote yourself if you are a nominee.
If you break this rule, you will be banned on voting for 24 hour and the list will corrected accordingly.

- if the list comes down to 2, it will be just subtract 1 and add 1. if the choice is yourself as nominee, you simply do nothing (can't vote).

- MONDAY Massacre.
On Monday, the point for subtraction is 2 (two) instead of 1 (one). The addition is still the same 1 (one) point.
If the nominee only has 1 point left on Monday, he/she can't be eliminated (no 2 points substration to minus point). It has to wait till Tuesday.

- The date and time is DinoRPG's date and time. Check the time on the game bar. Remember, you can only vote once in every 24 hours. If it is not so clear, I repeat you can NOT post/vote again until at least 24 hrs.

Special rules in regards of the Kingdom game:

- You can have only one title at a time. As above it will be the last nominee who will recieve that title, the first nominee to be oust out will also own a title (which will be secret, but something paired with).

- There will be 20 up to 30 nominees, you can't nominated yourself, and you can't vetoed being nominated. The game will always begin on Tuesday, when there's enough nominated names on the list. You can nominate up to two names.

- Then, when all titles are taken, all titled players will try to ascend to godhood.
